/* Title: c.wimpt
 * Purpose: provides low-level Wimp functionality
 * History: IDJ: 07-Feb-92: prepared for source release
 *          JAB: 22-Apr-92: added wimpt_messages and appended wimpt_init
 *                          accordingly
